      <title>Alantra因投资银行业务低迷而裁员德国员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/alantra-cuts-germany-staff-in-half-amid-investment-banking-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alantra Partners SA 已将其德国子公司的员工人数削减了约一半，这家西班牙公司在交易枯竭后重组了其投资银行业务。]]></description>
